// User-oriented-services mtlb specifically user k liyeh krna, mtlb aab koi common-cheez-pe-kaam-nhi-krna hai mtlb aab toh sirf user ki jo private-cheeze hai uspeh hi kaam krna hai, and yeh kaam user-k-jo-naukar hotehh hai voh krtehh hai, mtlb basically user ki application meh yeh 3-layers hoti hai joki user-orienteed-kaam krti hai, jaise creating-session , then converting/decrypting and showing and making requests. mtlb it is like jaise person1 person2 k flat meh toh puchgya ,now aab baki jo kaam hai,voh enn upper-layers(session,presentation,application-layer) ka kaam hai ki aab uss building meh puche huyehh person1 ko person2 se mila k liyeh jo bhi kaam krna hai voh aab enko hi krna hai.

